PN,41401
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1780650346
OL,3,CNew AI-designed vaccine 'could protect
OL,4,Cagainst whole families of viruses'
OL,6,FNew vaccine technology created with
OL,7,Fthe help of artificial intelligence
OL,8,Fcould provide immunity against whole
OL,9,Ffamilies of viruses and protect people
OL,10,Ffrom any future mutations in a single
OL,11,Fjab, according to scientists.
OL,13,FThe method could prevent pandemics
OL,14,Fbefore they begin, saving millions of
OL,15,Flives and helping countries avoid
OL,16,Flockdowns, researchers said.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/16
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,415,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1780650346
OL,3,CNew AI-designed vaccine 'could protect
OL,4,Cagainst whole families of viruses'
OL,6,FThe "super-antigen" is developed by
OL,7,Fusing machine learning that analyses
OL,8,Fpast and current outbreaks to
OL,9,Fdetermine what is essential for
OL,10,Fviruses to survive.
OL,12,FA world-first human trial has shown
OL,13,Fthat a coronavirus vaccine made using
OL,14,Fthe technology is safe, with more than
OL,15,F200 people set to be recruited for a
OL,16,Fphase II study.
OL,18,FExperts hailed the method as a "big
OL,19,Fparadigm change" to the current
OL,20,F"reactive" system which "struggles to
OL,21,Fkeep pace" as diseases evolve.
OL,26,@nD@EOUnD@SO]zD@`OU{D@PO]|D@AOU|D@JO]|D@
OL,26,AYOU}D@JO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/16
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,415,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1780650346
OL,3,CNew AI-designed vaccine 'could protect
OL,4,Cagainst whole families of viruses'
OL,6,FA phase I trial, published in the
OL,7,FJournal of Infection, included 49
OL,8,Fhealthy volunteers aged between 18 and
OL,9,F50 who had the vaccine in Cambridge
OL,10,Fand Southampton.
OL,12,FIt was administered as DNA vaccine
OL,13,Fthrough a micro fluid jet.
OL,15,FThis is a needle-free method that uses
OL,16,Fa high-pressure, hair-thin stream of
OL,17,Fliquid to push vaccine blueprints
OL,18,Fdirectly into skin cells.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/16
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,415,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1780650346
OL,3,CNew AI-designed vaccine 'could protect
OL,4,Cagainst whole families of viruses'
OL,6,FResearchers found the jab is safe and
OL,7,Fthat it triggered an immune response
OL,8,Fto not only SARS-CoV-2 and SARS, but
OL,9,Fto related bat viruses that could
OL,10,Fpotentially jump from animals to
OL,11,Fhumans.
OL,13,FA previous study in animals also found
OL,14,Fthe jab sparked a strong immune
OL,15,Fresponse against a range of
OL,16,Fcoronaviruses.
OL,18,FCurrent vaccines use antigens from
OL,19,Fspecific strains of virus that have
OL,20,Falready been detected in humans.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/16
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,415,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1780650346
OL,3,CNew AI-designed vaccine 'could protect
OL,4,Cagainst whole families of viruses'
OL,6,FHowever, the universal Sarbeco
OL,7,Fcoronavirus vaccine, developed by the
OL,8,FUniversity of Cambridge and
OL,9,Fbiotechnology company DIOSynVax,
OL,10,Fbrings together features that are
OL,11,Fcommon in the whole family of viruses.
OL,13,FThis is done by researchers taking all
OL,14,Favailable genetic sequence data on
OL,15,Fcoronaviruses logged by surveillance
OL,16,Fprogrammes around the world to create
OL,17,Fa "super antigen".
OL,26,@yD@COUyD@QO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/16
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,415,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1780650346
OL,3,CNew AI-designed vaccine 'could protect
OL,4,Cagainst whole families of viruses'
OL,6,FProf Saul Faust, of the University of
OL,7,FSouthampton and the trial's chief
OL,8,Finvestigator, said: "Viruses like
OL,9,Finfluenza, coronaviruses and the ebola
OL,10,Fgroup are evolving continuously and by
OL,11,Fthe time vaccines are rolled out, they
OL,12,Fmay be poorly matched ` the current
OL,13,F'reactive' vaccine system struggles to
OL,14,Fkeep pace.
OL,16,F"This new class of universal vaccines
OL,17,Fare future-proofed.
OL,26,@pD@UOUxD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/16
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,415,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1780650346
OL,3,CNew AI-designed vaccine 'could protect
OL,4,Cagainst whole families of viruses'
OL,6,F"They not only protect against many
OL,7,Fvariants simultaneously, but
OL,8,Fpotentially against related viruses
OL,9,Fthat haven't yet emerged and spilt
OL,10,Fover to humans.
OL,12,F"If we can develop and clinically
OL,13,Fadvance this new class of vaccines
OL,14,Fbefore a virus outbreak begins,
OL,15,Fmillions of lives could be saved,
OL,16,Flockdowns avoided and the economy
OL,17,Fpreserved."
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUyD@KO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/16
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,415,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1780650346
OL,3,CNew AI-designed vaccine 'could protect
OL,4,Cagainst whole families of viruses'
OL,6,FProfessor Jonathan Heeney, from the
OL,7,Flab of viral zoonotics at the
OL,8,FUniversity of Cambridge's Department
OL,9,Fof Veterinary Medicine, told the Press
OL,10,FAssociation: "What that Covid pandemic
OL,11,Ftaught us is how fast we can make
OL,12,Fvaccines, but we're still using the
OL,13,Fold paradigm.
OL,15,F"This is about making one vaccine that
OL,16,Fwill get them all based on their
OL,17,Frelationships."
OL,26,@rD@NOUwD@AOUyD@OO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G8/16
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,415,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41409
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1780650346
OL,3,CNew AI-designed vaccine 'could protect
OL,4,Cagainst whole families of viruses'
OL,6,FHe added: "You hoover up all the
OL,7,Fgenomic sequences; what's known from
OL,8,Faround the world, from past outbreaks
OL,9,Fand current outbreaks, and you do some
OL,10,Fbasic structural science.
OL,12,F"We take all these different
OL,13,Fsequences...and we think, 'OK, what's
OL,14,Fconsistent amongst them, what's not
OL,15,Fchanging, what is essential for their
OL,16,Flife' and that's what we target.
OL,26,@nD@KOUtD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G9/16
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,415,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41410
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1780650346
OL,3,CNew AI-designed vaccine 'could protect
OL,4,Cagainst whole families of viruses'
OL,6,F"It not only predicts, but it targets
OL,7,Fwhat is essential for that virus
OL,8,Ffamily. We're targeting something in a
OL,9,Fvirus family, which the virus can't
OL,10,Fchange easily."
OL,12,FA phase II trial is expected to
OL,13,Finclude "upwards of 200 or more
OL,14,Fpeople", Prof Heeney said.
OL,16,FHe is hopeful that the technology can
OL,17,Fbe a "game changer" that makes
OL,18,Fvaccines "far better, broader, and
OL,19,Fgive more robust protection".
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@OO]uD@IOUvD@GO]yD@FOUyD@SO]zD@
OL,26,AJOU{D@\O]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G10/16
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,415,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41411
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1780650346
OL,3,CNew AI-designed vaccine 'could protect
OL,4,Cagainst whole families of viruses'
OL,6,FIt could provide broad protection from
OL,7,Fthousands of variants of viruses, such
OL,8,Fas ebola.
OL,10,FProf Heeney told PA that during his
OL,11,Fcareer he has travelled during
OL,12,Foutbreaks, and the one that "really
OL,13,Fleft a mark" was the West African
OL,14,FEbola epidemic, which lasted from 2013
OL,15,Fto 2016.
OL,17,FThere is currently another epidemic of
OL,18,Febola happening in the Democratic
OL,19,FRepublic of the Congo (DRC) and
OL,20,FUganda, caused by bundibugyo virus.
OL,26,@tD@]OUuD@LO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G11/16
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,415,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41412
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1780650346
OL,3,CNew AI-designed vaccine 'could protect
OL,4,Cagainst whole families of viruses'
OL,6,F"There's a lot of viruses out there,
OL,7,Fand once we know them, we start
OL,8,Fchasing them, but we have to change
OL,9,Fthat paradigm," he said.
OL,11,F"And that's what this is about, it's
OL,12,Fabout making vaccines that not just
OL,13,Fprotect us from today's viruses, but
OL,14,Fthe ones that haven't yet happened.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@OO]sD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G12/16
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,415,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41413
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1780650346
OL,3,CNew AI-designed vaccine 'could protect
OL,4,Cagainst whole families of viruses'
OL,6,F"A great example of that is what's
OL,7,Fgoing on now in the DRC. Again, yet
OL,8,Fanother Ebola virus, but it's not the
OL,9,Fsame one, it's from the same family.
OL,10,FDeja vu. We're behind the curve, and
OL,11,Fthese viruses belong to the same
OL,12,Ffamily.
OL,14,F"So, what we're trying to do is to
OL,15,Fmake a vaccine that will protect
OL,16,Fagainst all those different viruses in
OL,17,Fa family, and it's a big paradigm
OL,18,Fchange."
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@AOUzD@HO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G13/16
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,415,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41414
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1780650346
OL,3,CNew AI-designed vaccine 'could protect
OL,4,Cagainst whole families of viruses'
OL,6,FThe team is also looking to advance on
OL,7,Fa vaccine for bird flu, which Prof
OL,8,FHeeney described as a "big global
OL,9,Fthreat".
OL,11,FHe said: "This is because this bird
OL,12,Fflu virus is all around the world, on
OL,13,Fmost continents, not only impacting
OL,14,Fbirds, but also mammals and humans,
OL,15,Fand it's even in the food chain in
OL,16,FAmerica, in milk.
OL,26,@pD@WOUqD@GO]sD@JOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G14/16
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,415,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41415
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1780650346
OL,3,CNew AI-designed vaccine 'could protect
OL,4,Cagainst whole families of viruses'
OL,6,F"So it's quite a worry, but there's
OL,7,Fdifferent clades, or types of
OL,8,Ffamilies, and there's particular ones
OL,9,Fin south-east Asia that are very
OL,10,Fdifferent, but that have killed people
OL,11,Fin double digits.
OL,13,F"So it's about making sure that our
OL,14,Ftechnology can get whatever is going
OL,15,Fto pop up and protect us, and to get
OL,16,Fahead of that curve, instead of
OL,17,Fchasing it."
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOUyD@LO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G15/16
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,415,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41416
SC,0016
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1780650346
OL,3,CNew AI-designed vaccine 'could protect
OL,4,Cagainst whole families of viruses'
OL,6,FProf Marian Knight, scientific
OL,7,Fdirector for National Institute for
OL,8,FHealth and Care Research (NIHR)
OL,9,FInfrastructure, said: "The remarkable
OL,10,Fsuccess of this AI-designed 'super-
OL,11,Fantigen' trial marks a pivotal leap
OL,12,Fforward in our ability to deliver
OL,13,Fbroad, lasting viral protection."
OL,15,FThe study was sponsored by University
OL,16,FHospital Southampton NHS Foundation
OL,17,FTrust.
OL,26,@qD@WOUuD@aO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G16/16
